comment:
* A representation of a smartspace event.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: EVENT_TARGET_SHOWN
variables.comment: * Smartspace target was brought into view.

variables.name: EVENT_TARGET_HIDDEN
variables.comment: * Smartspace target went out of view.

variables.name: EVENT_TARGET_DISMISS
variables.comment: * A dismiss action was issued by the user.

variables.name: EVENT_TARGET_BLOCK
variables.comment: * A block action was issued by the user.

variables.name: EVENT_UI_SURFACE_SHOWN
variables.comment: * The Ui surface came into view.

variables.name: EVENT_UI_SURFACE_HIDDEN
variables.comment: * The Ui surface went out of view.

methods.name: public SmartspaceTarget getSmartspaceTarget()
methods.comment: * Get the {@link SmartspaceTarget} associated with this event.

methods.name: public String getSmartspaceActionId()
methods.comment: * Get the action id of the Smartspace Action associated with this event.

methods.name: public int getEventType()
methods.comment: * Get the {@link EventType} of this event.
